ZH: 我的心脏在跳动。
EN: My heart is beating.

ZH: 她的心脏疼得厉害。
EN: Her heart is hurting badly.

ZH: 他的心脏病治好了。
EN: His heart disease has been cured.

ZH: 她拥有一颗健康的心脏。
EN: She has a healthy heart.

ZH: 医生听了我的心脏。
EN: The doctor listened to my heart.

ZH: 心脏是人体重要的器官之一。
EN: The heart is one of the vital organs in the human body.

ZH: 心脏负责泵血到全身各处。
EN: The heart is responsible for pumping blood throughout the body.

ZH: 运动对心脏健康很重要。
EN: Exercise is essential for a healthy heart.

ZH: 我的心脏病史已经持续多年了。
EN: I have had a history of heart disease for many years.

ZH: 心脏病是当今危害人类健康的常见疾病之一。
EN: Heart disease is one of the common health hazards in today's society.

ZH: 老人常常有心脏问题。
EN: Elderly people often have heart problems.

ZH: 我需要去医院做个心脏检查。
EN: I need to go to the hospital for a heart check-up.

ZH: 养成良好的生活习惯有助于保护心脏。
EN: Developing good lifestyle habits helps protect the heart.

ZH: 心脏手术需要经历一段复杂的康复期。
EN: Heart surgery requires a complex recovery period.

ZH: 她的心脏真是一切问题的根源。
EN: Her heart is truly the root of all problems.

ZH: 心脏太重要了，我们不能忽略它。
EN: The heart is too important for us to ignore.

ZH: 心脏骤然停止了跳动，他就永远离开了我们。
EN: His heart suddenly stopped beating, and he was forever gone from us.

ZH: 许多人因为心脏病而丧生。
EN: Many people die from heart disease.

ZH: 心脏是情感的象征。
EN: The heart is a symbol of emotions.
